➜邓超连发4条状态替孙俪庆生，亲手做蛋糕，还收集网友意见
http://www.sohu.com/a/422331882_100091227	44409
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>今天，是酸成柠檬精的吃瓜阿美。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">最近全网都知道孙俪要过39岁生日。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">只因为她老公，邓超。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201002/1a6610477ece4665b5e1062f817b466f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">26号是孙俪的生日，在这前一天<strong>邓超发布了一条礼物的征求意见微博。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201002/78d4450574074a1596cd0779a534e2af.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">然而评论的画风却是这样的——</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">张颜齐你怎么活跃地像个营销号到处蹦跶？！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201002/2b6022346cdf4ee0b8b07fd9cf2c68ea.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
